                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-grow text-left">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-main-accent mr-3 mt-1"></i>
                            <span class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed">3 sections essentielles (présentation simple uniquement)</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-main-accent mr-3 mt-1"></i>
                            <span class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed">Mini-galerie ou liste de services basique</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-main-accent mr-3 mt-1"></i>
                            <span class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed">Contact simple par email</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-main-accent mr-3 mt-1"></i>
                            <span class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed">Liens réseaux sociaux basiques</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
